OL,3,CProviding financial support to
OL,4,Cshipbuilder risked public money, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe Government has not stepped in to
OL,8,Foffer financial support to Belfast
OL,9,Fshipbuilder Harland and Wolff due to
OL,10,Fthe risk of losing of public money,
OL,11,Fthe Business Secretary has said.
OL,13,FThe company, which is part of a
OL,14,Fconsortium that landed a major
OL,15,Fcontract to build new Fleet Solid
OL,16,FSupport ships for the Royal Navy, had
OL,17,Fapplied for a #200million loan
OL,18,Fguarantee from the Government as part
OL,19,Fof efforts to restructure its finances.
