OL,4,Cshipbuilder risked public money, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FIn a written statement to Parliament,
OL,8,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,9,Fexplained why the Government had
OL,10,Frejected the request to act as a
OL,11,Fguarantor on fresh lending sought by
OL,12,Fthe company.
OL,14,FMr Reynolds said the Government would
OL,15,Falso not offer direct funding to help
OL,16,Fmaintain the company's liquidity.
