OL,3,CProviding financial support to
OL,4,Cshipbuilder risked public money, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,F"After a detailed review of an
OL,8,Fapplication by Harland and Wolff for a
OL,9,FUK Export Finance Export Development
OL,10,FGuarantee (EDG), His Majesty's
OL,11,FGovernment has decided not to proceed
OL,12,Fwith the provision of a guarantee,"
OL,13,Fwrote Mr Reynolds.
OL,15,F"This decision was based on a
OL,16,Fcomprehensive assessment of the
OL,17,Fcompany's financial profile and the
OL,18,Fcriteria set out in our risk policies.
OL,19,FWe have also decided not to provide
OL,20,Fany form of emergency liquidity
OL,21,Ffunding.
