OL,3,CProviding financial support to
OL,4,Cshipbuilder risked public money, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,F"While such a decision is not easy, it
OL,8,Fis my assessment, following extensive
OL,9,Fengagement by my officials with market
OL,10,Fplayers, that HM Government funding
OL,11,Fwould not necessarily secure our
OL,12,Fobjectives and there is a very
OL,13,Fsubstantial risk that taxpayer money
OL,14,Fwould be lost.
OL,16,F"The Government believes, in this
OL,17,Finstance, that the market is best
OL,18,Fplaced to resolve the commercial
OL,19,Fmatters faced by Harland and Wolff."
