OL,4,Cshipbuilder risked public money, says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FHarland and Wolff, which famously
OL,8,Fbuilt the Titanic, has four sites `
OL,9,Fone in Belfast, two in Scotland
OL,10,F(Methil on the Firth of Forth and
OL,11,FArnish on the Isle of Lewis) and one
OL,12,Fin England (Appledore in north Devon).
OL,14,FIn a statement on Friday confirming
OL,15,Fthat the Government loan guarantee had
OL,16,Fbeen rejected, the company said it
OL,17,Fwould seek alternative new debt
OL,18,Ffacilities from current lender
OL,19,FRiverstone Credit Management.
