OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe company said it was also engaging
OL,8,Fan investment bank ` Rothschild & Co `
OL,9,Fto assess "strategic options".
OL,11,FAmid ongoing uncertainty around the
OL,12,Fshipbuilder's future, the company also
OL,13,Fannounced that chief executive John
OL,14,FWood was taking a leave of absence
OL,15,Fwith immediate effect.
OL,17,FHarland and Wolff said Russell Downs,
OL,18,Fan industry expert in refinancing and
OL,19,Frecapitalisation, would take on the
OL,20,Frole of interim executive chairman.
