OL,7,FCommenting on the company's move to
OL,8,Fseek further financing from
OL,9,FRiverstone, Mr Reynolds said: "This
OL,10,Fshould allow the business to continue
OL,11,Fpursuing its short and longer-term
OL,12,Fobjectives, in which the Government
OL,13,Fcontinues to take an interest.
OL,15,F"In all our engagements with them,
OL,16,FRiverstone Credit Management LLC has
OL,17,Frecognised the importance of the
OL,18,Fassets at Harland and Wolff as well as
OL,19,Fthe people who work there, showing a
OL,20,Fdesire to find pragmatic solutions
OL,21,Fthat support HM Government objectives.
