OL,7,F"Harland and Wolff indicates that
OL,8,Fthese discussions on new financing
OL,9,Fshould conclude in the next few days.
OL,10,FThis will involve the current CEO
OL,11,Ftaking an immediate leave of absence
OL,12,Fand the onboarding of new management
OL,13,Fwith a focus on recapitalisation and
OL,14,Fensuring sustainable finances."
