OL,8,Fsaid: "Harland and Wolff's workforce
OL,9,Fand the shipyards they work in are of
OL,10,Fcritical strategic importance. Five
OL,11,Fyears after Unite members secured
OL,12,FHarland and Wolff's survival in
OL,13,FBelfast, the political focus must now
OL,14,Fbe on attracting stakeholders who are
OL,15,Fcommitted to building a long-term
OL,16,Ffuture, rather than those looking to
OL,17,Fturn a quick profit.
